    "subtype": "equipment",
    "text": "*Resilient* runes imbue armor with additional protective magic. This grants the wearer a +1 item bonus to saving throws. You can upgrade the *resilient rune* already etched on a suit of armor using the normal process for upgrading items and runes.",
    "traits": [
      {
        "alternate_link": {
